00:47:45,800 --> 00:47:51,200
and you show that in your body language, then 
it makes the other person much more receptive  

554
00:47:51,200 --> 00:47:57,320
to hearing whatever you have to say. Then I think 
the other piece is that you've got to be direct. 

555
00:47:57,320 --> 00:48:01,880
The worst feedback is the kind of 
passive-aggressive feedback versus saying  

